  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Migration to Version 8.0.23</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>迁移到版本 8.0.23</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
    A dump/restore is not required for those running 8.0.X.
    However, if you are upgrading from a version earlier than 8.0.22,
    see <xref linkend="release-8-0-22">.
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
运行8.0.X的用户不需要转储/恢复。不过，如果你是从一个早于8.0.22的版本升级而来，
那么请参阅<xref linkend="release-8-0-22">。
</para>

  </sect2>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Changes</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>修改列表</title>

   <itemizedlist>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Protect against indirect security threats caused by index functions
      changing session-local state (Gurjeet Singh, Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
防止由索引函数改变会话本地状态引起的间接安全风险 (Gurjeet Singh, Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This change prevents allegedly-immutable index functions from possibly
      subverting a superuser's session (CVE-2009-4136).
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个修改阻止早已不变的索引函数可能破坏超级用户的会话 (CVE-2009-4136)。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Reject SSL certificates containing an embedded null byte in the common
      name (CN) field (Magnus)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
拒绝SSL证书在公用名（CN）字段包含一个嵌入的空字节 (Magnus)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This prevents unintended matching of a certificate to a server or client
      name during SSL validation (CVE-2009-4034).
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这阻止了在SSL验证期间无意识的匹配证书到服务器或客户端名 (CVE-2009-4034)。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible crash during backend-startup-time cache initialization (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复后端启动时缓存初始化期间可能的崩溃 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent signals from interrupting <literal>VACUUM</> at unsafe times
      (Alvaro)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
阻止信号在不安全的时间打断<literal>VACUUM</> (Alvaro)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This fix prevents a PANIC if a <literal>VACUUM FULL</> is canceled
      after it's already committed its tuple movements, as well as transient
      errors if a plain <literal>VACUUM</> is interrupted after having
      truncated the table.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个修改阻止了<literal>VACUUM FULL</>在它已经提交了它的元组移动之后取消时的恐慌，
还有简单<literal>VACUUM</>在已经截断表之后中断时的瞬态错误。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible crash due to integer overflow in hash table size
      calculation (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复哈希表尺寸估算中由于整数溢出引起的崩溃 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This could occur with extremely large planner estimates for the size of
      a hashjoin's result.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这可能在哈希连接的结果有非常大的规划器估算时发生。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix very rare crash in <type>inet</>/<type>cidr</> comparisons (Chris
      Mikkelson)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<type>inet</>/<type>cidr</>比较中非常罕见的崩溃 (Chris Mikkelson)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix premature drop of temporary files used for a cursor that is accessed
      within a subtransaction (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复用于在一个子事务中可以访问的游标的临时文件过早删除 (Heikki)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix PAM password processing to be more robust (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复PAM口令处理，使其更加健壮 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The previous code is known to fail with the combination of the Linux
      <literal>pam_krb5</> PAM module with Microsoft Active Directory as the
      domain controller.  It might have problems elsewhere too, since it was
      making unjustified assumptions about what arguments the PAM stack would
      pass to it.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
都知道以前的代码未能组合Linux <literal>pam_krb5</> PAM模块和Microsoft Active Directory
作为域控制器。可能在其他的地方也有问题，
因为它对于将传递哪个PAM堆栈参数做了不公平的假设。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix rare crash in exception processing in PL/Python (Peter)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复PL/Python中异常处理时罕见的崩溃 (Peter)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure <application>psql</>'s flex module is compiled with the correct
      system header definitions (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
确保<application>psql</>的flex模块是用正确的系统头定义编译的 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This fixes build failures on platforms where
      <literal>-&minus;enable-largefile</> causes incompatible changes in the
      generated code.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这修复了<literal>--enable-largefile</>
导致在生成的代码中有不兼容的更改的平台上编译失败的问题。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Make the postmaster ignore any <literal>application_name</> parameter in
      connection request packets, to improve compatibility with future libpq
      versions (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
让主进程忽略任何连接请求包中的<literal>application_name</>参数，
以提升与未来libpq版本的兼容性 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Update time zone data files to <application>tzdata</> release 2009s
      for DST law changes in Antarctica, Argentina, Bangladesh, Fiji,
      Novokuznetsk, Pakistan, Palestine, Samoa, Syria; also historical
      corrections for Hong Kong.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
更新时区数据文件到<application>tzdata</>版本2009s，
因为DST规律已经在Antarctica, Argentina, Bangladesh, Fiji,
Novokuznetsk, Pakistan, Palestine, Samoa, Syria改变了；
也修正了Hong Kong的历史时间。
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

