<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix <function>EXTRACT(EPOCH)</> for
<type>TIME WITH TIME ZONE</> values</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
为<type>TIME WITH TIME ZONE</>值修复<function>EXTRACT(EPOCH)</>
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix mis-display of negative fractional seconds in
