<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
This error only occurred when the
<literal>-&minus;enable-integer-datetimes</> configuration switch had been used.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个错误只在使用了<literal>--enable-integer-datetimes</> 配置开关时发生。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix pg_dump to dump trigger names containing <literal>%</>
