    <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> libraries, so it might be
    necessary to re-link some user applications if they cannot
    find the properly-numbered shared library.
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
运行8.0.*的用户不需要转储/恢复。这个版本更新<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>
库的主版本号，所以如果他们不能找到正确编号的共享库，
可能需要重新连接一些用户应用。
</para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Changes</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>修改列表</title>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Increment the major version number of all interface
libraries (Bruce)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
增加所有接口库的主版本号 (Bruce)
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
This should have been done in 8.0.0.  It is required so 7.4.X versions
of PostgreSQL client applications, like <application>psql</>,
can be used on the same machine as 8.0.X applications.  This might require
re-linking user applications that use these libraries.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这应该在8.0.0中完成。它需要7.4.X版本的PostgreSQL客户端应用，
像<application>psql</>，可以用在和8.0.X应用相同的机器上。
这可能需要重新连接使用这些库的用户应用。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Add Windows-only <varname>wal_sync_method</> setting of
<option>fsync_writethrough</> (Magnus, Bruce)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
添加仅Windows的<varname>wal_sync_method</>设置<option>fsync_writethrough</>  (Magnus, Bruce)
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
This setting causes <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> to write through
any disk-drive write cache when writing to WAL.
This behavior was formerly called <option>fsync</>, but was
renamed because it acts quite differently from <option>fsync</> on other
platforms.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个设置导致写入WAL时<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>透写任何磁盘驱动的写缓存。
这个行为以前称为<option>fsync</>，但是已经重命名了，
因为它在其他平台上表现的与<option>fsync</>稍微有点不同。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Enable the <varname>wal_sync_method</> setting of
<option>open_datasync</> on Windows, and make it the default for that
 platform (Magnus, Bruce)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
在Windows上启用<varname>wal_sync_method</>设置<option>open_datasync</>，
并让它成为那个平台的缺省 (Magnus, Bruce)
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
Because the default is no longer <option>fsync_writethrough</>,
data loss is possible during a power failure if the disk drive has
write caching enabled. To turn off the write cache on Windows,
from the <application>Device Manager</>, choose the drive properties,
then <literal>Policies</>.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
因为缺省不再是<option>fsync_writethrough</>，如果磁盘驱动启用了写缓存，
那么在电源故障期间的数据丢失是有可能的。在Windows上要关闭写缓存，
从<application>Device Manager</>中，选择该驱动属性，然后<literal>Policies</>。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>New cache management algorithm <acronym>2Q</> replaces
<acronym>ARC</> (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
新增缓存管理算法<acronym>2Q</>替代<acronym>ARC</> (Tom)
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
This was done to avoid a pending US patent on <acronym>ARC</>.  The
<acronym>2Q</> code might be a few percentage points slower than
<acronym>ARC</> for some work loads.  A better cache management algorithm
will appear in 8.1.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这样做是为了避免在<acronym>ARC</>上挂起US执照。
<acronym>2Q</>代码比<acronym>ARC</>对于某些工作负载可能有几个百分点的缓慢。
一个更好的缓存管理算法将在8.1中出现。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Planner adjustments to improve behavior on freshly-created
tables (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
规划器调整以改善自由创建的表上的行为 (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Allow plpgsql to assign to an element of an array that is
initially <literal>NULL</> (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
允许plpgsql分配初始为<literal>NULL</>的数组元素 (Tom)
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
Formerly the array would remain <literal>NULL</>, but now it becomes a
single-element array.  The main SQL engine was changed to handle
<command>UPDATE</> of a null array value this way in 8.0, but the similar
case in plpgsql was overlooked.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
以前该数组将保持<literal>NULL</>，但是现在它变成一个单元素数组。
在8.0中主要的SQL引擎改变为以这种方式处理一个空数组值的<command>UPDATE</>，
但是plpgsql中相似的情况则被忽视了。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Convert <literal>\r\n</> and <literal>\r</> to <literal>\n</>
in plpython function bodies (Michael Fuhr)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
在plpython函数体中转换<literal>\r\n</>和<literal>\r</>为<literal>\n</> (Michael Fuhr)
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
 This prevents syntax errors when plpython code is written on a Windows or
 Mac client.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这阻止了plpython代码是在Windows或Mac客户端上写的时的语法错误。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Allow SPI cursors to handle utility commands that return rows,
such as <command>EXPLAIN</> (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
允许SPI游标处理返回行的工具命令，比如<command>EXPLAIN</> (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix <command>CLUSTER</> failure after <command>ALTER TABLE
SET WITHOUT OIDS</> (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<command>ALTER TABLE SET WITHOUT OIDS</>之后的<command>CLUSTER</>失败 (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Reduce memory usage of <command>ALTER TABLE ADD COLUMN</>
(Neil)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
减少<command>ALTER TABLE ADD COLUMN</>的内存使用 (Neil)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix <command>ALTER LANGUAGE RENAME</> (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<command>ALTER LANGUAGE RENAME</> (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Document the Windows-only <literal>register</> and
<literal>unregister</> options of <application>pg_ctl</> (Magnus)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
记录仅Windows的<application>pg_ctl</>的<literal>register</>和<literal>unregister</>选项 (Magnus)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Ensure operations done during backend shutdown are counted by
statistics collector</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
确保后端关闭期间所做的操作都被统计收集器计数
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
This is expected to resolve reports of <application>pg_autovacuum</>
not vacuuming the system catalogs often enough &mdash; it was not being
told about catalog deletions caused by temporary table removal during
backend exit.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这是预计解决<application>pg_autovacuum</>不够频繁的清理系统目录的报告&mdash;
没有告诉后端关闭期间临时表删除引起的目录删除。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Change the Windows default for configuration parameter
<varname>log_destination</> to <option>eventlog</> (Magnus)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
为配置参数<varname>log_destination</>到<option>eventlog</>
修改Windows缺省 (Magnus)
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
By default, a server running on Windows will now send log output to the
Windows event logger rather than standard error.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
缺省的，运行在Windows上的服务器现在将发送日志输出到windows事件记录器而不是标准误差。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Make Kerberos authentication work on Windows (Magnus)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
让Kerberos认证在Windows上工作 (Magnus)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Allow <command>ALTER DATABASE RENAME</> by superusers
who aren't flagged as having CREATEDB privilege (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
允许没有被标记为拥有CREATEDB权限的超级用户<command>ALTER DATABASE RENAME</> (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Modify WAL log entries for <command>CREATE</> and
<command>DROP DATABASE</> to not specify absolute paths (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
为<command>CREATE</>和<command>DROP DATABASE</>修改WAL日志条目，
不指定绝对路径 (Tom)
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>This allows point-in-time recovery on a different machine with possibly
different database location.  Note that <command>CREATE TABLESPACE</> still
poses a hazard in such situations.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这允许不同机器上的时间点恢复可以有不同的数据库位置。请注意，
<command>CREATE TABLESPACE</>在这种情况下仍然构成了风险。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix crash from a backend exiting with an open transaction
that created a table and opened a cursor on it (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复后端带有创建了一个表并且在它上面打开了一个游标的打开的事务退出时的崩溃 (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix <function>array_map()</> so it can call PL functions
(Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<function>array_map()</>，这样它可以调用PL函数 (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Several <filename>contrib/tsearch2</> and
<filename>contrib/btree_gist</> fixes (Teodor)
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
几个<filename>contrib/tsearch2</>和<filename>contrib/btree_gist</>修复 (Teodor)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix crash of some <filename>contrib/pgcrypto</>
functions on some platforms (Marko Kreen)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复某些平台上一些<filename>contrib/pgcrypto</>函数的崩溃 (Marko Kreen)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix <filename>contrib/intagg</> for 64-bit platforms
(Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
为64位平台修复<filename>contrib/intagg</> (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix ecpg bugs in parsing of <command>CREATE</> statement
(Michael)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复解析<command>CREATE</>语句时的ecpg错误 (Michael)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Work around gcc bug on powerpc and amd64 causing problems in
ecpg (Christof Petig)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
绕开在ecpg上导致问题的powerpc和amd64上的gcc错误 (Christof Petig)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Do not use locale-aware versions of <function>upper()</>,
<function>lower()</>, and <function>initcap()</> when the locale is
<literal>C</> (Bruce)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
当本地环境是<literal>C</>时，不要使用<function>upper()</>、
<function>lower()</>和<function>initcap()</>的对本地敏感的版本 (Bruce)
</para>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
 This allows these functions to work on platforms that generate errors
 for non-7-bit data when the locale is <literal>C</>.
</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这允许这些函数在本地环境是<literal>C</>时，在为非7位的数据产生错误的平台上工作。
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix <function>quote_ident()</> to quote names that match keywords (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<function>quote_ident()</>，以便给匹配关键字的名字加引号 (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix <function>to_date()</> to behave reasonably when
<literal>CC</> and <literal>YY</> fields are both used (Karel)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<function>to_date()</>，以在<literal>CC</>和<literal>YY</>
字段都使用了时合理的行为 (Karel)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Prevent <function>to_char(interval)</> from failing
when given a zero-month interval (Tom)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
当给出一个0月的间隔时，阻止<function>to_char(interval)</>失败 (Tom)
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>Fix wrong week returned by <function>date_trunc('week')</>
(Bruce)</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<function>date_trunc('week')</>返回的错误星期
</para>
