      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
让<varname>log_duration</>只在<varname>log_statement</>输出查询时输出 (Ed L.)
</para>
     </listitem>

    </itemizedlist>
   </sect3>


   <sect3>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<title>Query Changes</title>
